    <string name="turn_mechanic_1">Each player rolls 6 dice on their turn.</string>
    <string name="turn_mechanic_2">After each roll, you must set aside at least one scoring die.</string>
    <string name="turn_mechanic_3">You can choose to reroll the remaining dice to accumulate more points.</string>
    <string name="turn_mechanic_4">If you roll no scoring dice, you lose all points accumulated that turn and pass to the next player.</string>
    <string name="turn_mechanic_5">You can choose to \'bank\' at any time and add accumulated points to your total.</string>
    <string name="turn_mechanic_6">If you use all 6 dice for scoring, you get a new roll with all dice.</string>

